originalText.text: Stay away from here if you see a black lady bar tending. She is the most insufferable, disrespectful person you will ever meet. She is rude to her customers, demands tips, and publicly outs you if she doesn't like you. Every time I've been to Josie's while she's working it's been a nightmare. She's always causing a scene. I'm not sure how this woman is still employed because everyone hates her. Who in the world refuses to serve water without a tip?? I'm sober trying to enjoy the night out with my friends and play some pool.
